column9: Experience a high-performance clean on hard floors and carpets with the Dirt Devil Multi-Surface Total Pet+ upright vacuum. The versatile Pet Tool Kit is designed to help easily remove pet hair throughout the home using versatile tools and extra cleaning reach. The 4-level height adjustment helps to smoothly transition between varying floor types with the turn of a dial. The included 12" Extension Wand, 11" 2-in-1 Crevice/Dusting Brush, Pet Upholstery Tool and Turbo Tool™ help target messes for above-floor cleaning. With Click Lock™ tool security, tools are locked into place so they won't fall off and are easily accessible in the middle of cleaning. Once finished, easily empty the large dirt cup with a one-touch button. CLEAN FASTER WITH MAX POWER TECHNOLOGY Get more suction and superior pick up in each pass.

column3: Dyson DC41 Upright Ball Vacuum (Certified Refurbished)
column9: This certified refurbished Dyson DC41 Upright Ball Vacuum is engineered for outstanding cleaning performance and ease of use. It has the strongest suction at the cleaner head, which automatically self-adjusts for different carpet lengths and hard floors. The DC41 features Dyson’s latest Radial Root Cyclone technology, Ball technology for smooth steering, and a large 0.55-gallon bin. Ball technology for upright vacuums Dyson Ball upright vacuums ride on a ball, which pivots on the spot so you can steer with a turn of the wrist. The ball also houses core technology, including the motor and ducting. There’s less clutter, so it’s easier to clean in awkward places, along edges, and around furniture. Strongest suction at the cleaner head Many upright vacuums use fixed settings, and their cleaner heads don’t self-adjust to different floor types. The bigger the gap between cleaner head and floor, the more suction power is wasted. With the DC41, an active base plate creates the optimal cleaner head contact for every floor type, reducing air leaks and retaining more suction power. It’s designed for outstanding performance across all floors--not just carpets. Powerful and durable The DC41 is constructed from materials selected for strength, flexibility, and tolerance. Many parts are made from polypropylene reinforced with 20 percent glass fibers and high-impact PC-ABS. Using these materials means greater strength from less plastic, so the machine is lightweight. Motorized brush bar Stiff nylon bristles spin at up to 90 times per second to agitate carpet pile and dislodge ground-in dirt and pet hair, and the brush bar can be turned off to protect delicate rugs and hard floors. Captures allergens and expels cleaner air Unlike ordinary vacuums that can’t always retain all the dust they remove, venting some of it back into your room in the air they expel, the DC41 captures and contains microscopic particles such as pollen, mold and bacteria.Hygienic and quick to emptyEmptying the bin on a Dyson vacuum is quick and hygienic. The bin is clear, so you can see when it needs emptying and how much dust, dirt, and pet hair the machine has captured. Just press the release button to empty the bin.

Enzymes are bad for sheepskin, because they break down protein, which is what wool and leather are made of. A formula that is neutral pH and without enzymes is not enough when you also care about what chemicals are in your laundry detergent. column3: Smart Choice Granite Countertop Dishwasher Installation Kit
column9: Granite Countertop Dishwasher Installation Kit facilitates the installation of an undercounter dishwasher without the need to drill holes for mounting screws. It is approved for granite, quartz, acrylic and other solid surface countertops. Kit comes with 2 dishwasher brackets and hardware.Installation Instructions1. Fully clean the mounting area on the underside of the countertop using an alcohol-based solution. 2. Open the dishwasher door to expose the dishwasher mounting brackets.3. Install the adhesive tabs supplied in the kit using the supplied set screw to each of the dishwasher mounting brackets.4. Once installed to the dishwasher, peel back a corner of the red protective liner to make for easier removal once underneath the countertop. 5. With the adhesive tabs installed, position the dishwasher underneath the countertop to the correct depth, and left to right adjustment. Once the dishwasher is in position, completely remove the red liner.6. Firmly hand press the adhesive tabs to the countertop and hold for a 30 second count. Then with a clamping aid, clamp the adhesive tabs in place for 5 minutes. Once 5 minutes has elapsed, the bond is set and will cure to its permanent bond in one hour.

column3: Cascade ActionPacs Dishwasher Detergent, Fresh Scent, 85-Count
column9: Product Description Cascade ActionPacs power away greasy residue for sparkling dishes in one easy-to-use, premeasured pac. ActionPacs combine the scrubbing power of Cascade and the grease-fighting power of Dawn to leave your dishes virtually spotless with a brilliant shine. Formulated with built-in rinse aid action plus water softeners to help prevent hard water deposits on glasses, ActionPacs dissolve in your dishwasher to leave virtually no mess—only sparkling dishes. Simply load your machine, pop in a pac, and go! From the Manufacturer Rinses away residue to leave dishes sparkling. view larger Formulated with the grease-fighting power of Dawn. For dish cleaning that packs concentrated cleaning power, try Cascade ActionPacs dish detergent. ActionPacs combine the scrubbing power of Cascade and the grease fighting power of Dawn to leave your dishes virtually spotless with a brilliant shine in one easy-to-use, pre-measured pac. Formulated with built-in rinse aid action plus water softeners to help prevent hard water deposits on glasses, ActionPacs dissolve in your dishwasher to leave virtually no mess—only sparkling dishes. Simply load your machine, pop in a pac, and go!3 Steps to Your Perfect Clean view largerFor a virtually no-fail clean, try Cascade’s ultimate dish routine.Cascade Platinum – Use every wash for a brilliant clean that even helps keep your dishwasher sparkling.Cascade Complete Rinse Aid – Fill your dishwasher’s rinse aid dispenser and refill as needed.Cascade Dishwasher Cleaner – Use once per month.Beyond Detergent view largerSecret ingredients for added shine, protection & performance.Cascade Rinse Aid – Protects glassware from spots and filming and delivers a dazzling dose of shine.Cascade Dishwasher Cleaner – Easy-to-use pacs help remove limescale buildup, grease, and odors lurking in your dishwasher.Frequently Asked QuestionsHow much Cascade detergent should I use in my dishwasher?For Cascade powder and gel detergents, start by trying the recommended amount on the back label. There may be times when it’s necessary to use a little more or less, depending on your dish load and water hardness. For something even simpler, try Cascade ActionPacs. Each pac provides the perfect dose of clean, so you know exactly how much to use, every time.How do ActionPacs work?Cascade, Cascade Complete, and Cascade Platinum ActionPacs make dishwashing even simpler by taking out the guesswork. They’re easy to use because they require no measuring, unwrapping, crumbling, or cleanup. ActionPacs contain a higher concentration of detergents than powders and gels, plus built-in rinse and shine ingredients. To use, simply pop an ActionPac into your dishwasher’s detergent cup, close the cup lid, and let your dishwasher run.My dishwasher manual says to fill both cups with detergent. Do I need to use two ActionPacs?Nope. You only need one ActionPac because the formula is concentrated. They’re designed to give you a convenient, simple way to dose detergent with no premeasuring.Do I need to pre-rinse my dishes?Actually, with Cascade Complete powder, gel, and ActionPacs, and Cascade Platinum ActionPacs, you can skip the pre-scrub and load your dishes in right off the table. These formulas contain advanced cleaning and rinsing power, so pre-rinsing isn’t necessary.What if I have hard water?Water hardness varies depending on where you live. The good news is all of our ActionPacs are formulated with water softeners to help fight hard water deposits on your dishes.How can I prevent filming on my glasses and dishware?Here are some simple steps you can take to help keep your glasses film-free:Fill both detergent cups for each load (if you’re using Cascade ActionPacs, you only need to use one).Try using Cascade Rinse Aid, which protects surfaces and boosts drying to prevent spots and streaks.Dishwasher water temperature should be at least 120 degrees Fahrenheit. Try running hot water at the kitchen sink before starting the load to help reach this temperature.To help prevent low water pressure, make sure that no other water is being used in the house (showers, grass watering, washing machine, etc.).Be sure the dishwasher is loaded so that no items block the sprayer arms and prevent adequate water from reaching all the dishes.Once a month, use Cascade Dishwasher Cleaner to help remove limescale, grease, and odor buildup that can contribute to spotting and filming.Product Comparison Cascade Platinum Cascade Complete Cascade Our ultimate clean for dishes, and even helps keep dishwasher sparkling. Powers away 24-hour stuck-on food—no pre-rinse needed. Rinses away residue to leave dishes sparkling. Grease-Fighting Power of Dawn ✓ ✓ ✓ Fights Tea & Coffee Stains ✓ ✓ ✓ Brilliant Shine ✓ ✓ ✓ Virtually Spotless Dishes Best Best Better Tough Food Enzyme Action Best Better Good Our Best Film Prevention for Sparkling Machine ✓

column9: Tired of stubborn odors that never seem to wash out of your clothes? Introducing Downy Rinse & Refresh laundry odor remover and fabric softener, a breakthrough laundry odor remover that helps rinse away the smelly residue trapped within fabric fibers. Add Downy Scent Booster Beads to your routine for extra freshness. *Vs. detergent alone. *Vs. the leading value brand in 3 washes. About Us The agitation, spinning, and heat of the laundry process can damage clothes at the fiber level. But Downy Fabric Softener smooths and strengthens fibers to protect clothes from the damage of the wash, helping them maintain their shape. By smoothing fibers, Downy reduces the friction between them that causes them to break and leads to pills and fuzz. And when fibers break, colors appear duller, so using Downy also helps keep your clothes from fading.

column9: Finally, long-lasting scent that is not overpowering. Downy Light Laundry Scent Booster Beads are small, lightly scented laundry beads that give you all-day Downy freshness. They’re made with no heavy perfumes, dyes, or phosphates… Plus, the Ocean Mist scent has the lightweight scent of fresh air and a crisp ocean breeze for a true escape-worthy freshness for everyone. With detergent alone, the freshness of your clothes can fade after taking them out of the wash. Using Downy laundry booster beads gives your laundry 4x the long-lasting freshness than with the leading detergent alone, so you can be confident in fresh-smelling clothes all day long. They can be used on all colors and fabrics and are safe to use in all washing machines. These laundry scent beads are easy to use; just start by tossing them right into the washer drum before adding your clothing. Use as much or as little as you want to get your desired level of freshness. Looking for more ways to keep your clothes fresh? Add Downy fabric softener and dryer laundry sheets to your routine for added softness. About Us The agitation, spinning, and heat of the laundry process can damage clothes at the fiber level. But Downy Fabric Softener smooths and strengthens fibers to protect clothes from the damage of the wash, helping them maintain their shape. By smoothing fibers, Downy reduces the friction between them that causes them to break and leads to pills and fuzz. And when fibers break, colors appear duller, so using Downy also helps keep your clothes from fading.

column9: Add a gentler and scentless softness to your laundry with Downy Free & Gentle Fabric Softener. The hypoallergenic and dermatologist-tested formula is recognized by the National Eczema Association and National Psoriasis Foundation*. With no dyes and perfumes, Downy Fabric Softener was made for those with sensitive skin. Enjoy the Downy softness you know and love with fewer wrinkles and less static. Downy Liquid Fabric Softener is compatible with all top- and front-loading HE machines. It's easy to use—after adding your favorite laundry detergent, pour Downy Liquid Fabric Softener into the fabric softener dispenser drawer or directly into the agitator and start the washer on your preferred cycle. Have clothes that feel softer and look newer** with Downy Free & Gentle Fabric Softener. About Us The agitation, spinning, and heat of the laundry process can damage clothes at the fiber level. But Downy Fabric Softener smooths and strengthens fibers to protect clothes from the damage of the wash, helping them maintain their shape. By smoothing fibers, Downy reduces the friction between them that causes them to break and leads to pills and fuzz. And when fibers break, colors appear duller, so using Downy also helps keep your clothes from fading.

column3: Downy Ultra Laundry Liquid Fabric Softener (Fabric Conditioner), April Fresh, 140 fl oz, 190 Loads
column9: Give your clothes a softer feel and a long-lasting floral scent with Downy April Fresh Fabric Softener. Downy Fabric Softener protects your clothes from stretching, fading, and fuzz while adding the signature April Fresh scent. Enjoy 3X more freshness* with less static and fewer wrinkles after every wash. Downy Liquid Fabric Softener is compatible with all top- and front-loading HE machines. It's easy to use—after adding your favorite laundry detergent, pour Downy Liquid Fabric Softener into the fabric softener dispenser drawer or directly into the agitator and start the washer on your preferred cycle. Feel softer, smell fresher, and look newer** with Downy 7-in-1 Fabric Softener. About Us The agitation, spinning, and heat of the laundry process can damage clothes at the fiber level. But Downy Fabric Softener smooths and strengthens fibers to protect clothes from the damage of the wash, helping them maintain their shape. By smoothing fibers, Downy reduces the friction between them that causes them to break and leads to pills and fuzz. And when fibers break, colors appear duller, so using Downy also helps keep your clothes from fading.
